asgn1Collection

Interface Listing

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    MovieListing

    public interface Listing
    Interface to support documents or works that make up the asgn1Collection.Collection We assume that a title, year of creation and keyword list are available for each listing
    Author:
    hogan
